        "meta_description": "A battery made from zinc and lignin that can be used over 8000 times. This has been developed by researchers at LiU with a vision to provide a cheap and sustainable battery solution for countries where access to electricity is limited.",
        "meta_lang": "en",
        "meta_favicon": "/favicon.ico",
